00:00:24.112 --> 00:00:26.322
had a pulse going up and down.

00:00:26.322 --> 00:00:28.475
This circuit has a real
interesting side effect

00:00:28.475 --> 00:00:30.940
when this switch opens up.

00:00:30.940 --> 00:00:33.083
So, let me give you a
couple of examples first,

00:00:33.083 --> 00:00:35.140
some practical examples of where

00:00:35.140 --> 00:00:37.367
