When you put a pulse of current into this,

00:01:01.950 --> 00:01:04.533
what happens is, the rod moves.

00:01:06.952 --> 00:01:08.912
The rod will move back and forth,

00:01:08.912 --> 00:01:11.089
so this is a way, for
instance, a doorbell.

00:01:11.089 --> 00:01:14.339
A doorbell has this kind of a actuator.

00:01:18.349 --> 00:01:21.197
Another kind of device
